Class SocketInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.msocket.SocketInfo

  • public class SocketInfo
extends Object
    This class keeps the information about each flowpath. It stores the socket, dataChannel sequence number of data flowing through that flowpath.
